msgstr "10800:Most 3D girls were really bossy and arrogant. She was a rare exception.[%p]"

msgid "10900:こんなかわいくて性格がよさそうな子が現実にいるはずがない。これは……演技だ！[%p]"
msgstr "10900:No 3D girl could possibly be this cute and kind. It was all an act![%p]"

msgid "11000:断ってやる。男らしくズバンと言ってやる……！[%p]"
msgstr "11000:I was going to say no. I was going to come out and say it clearly, like a man![%p]"

msgid "11100:[name]優愛[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "11100:[name]優愛[line]...[%p]"

msgid "11200:顔を上げた優愛の、眼鏡の奥に見える目は潤んでいた。[%p]"
msgstr "11200:She looked up at me, and I could see that her eyes were damp.[%p]"

msgid "11300:もしかして、泣いてるの？[linebreak]僕が無言だから？[linebreak]僕が泣かした？[%p]"
msgstr "11300:Was she crying? Because I didn't say anything? Had I made her cry?[%p]"

msgid "11400:ひええ、か、勘弁してよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "11400:Please, anything but that.[%p]"

msgid "11500:こんな修羅場、ゲームでしか経験したことないよ。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:I'd only ever experienced anything like this in video games.[%p]"

msgid "11600:すごくドキドキしてきた。しかも罪悪感まである。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:My heart was pounding really fast. I even felt guilty.[%p]"

msgid "11700:女の涙は武器になるってよく言うけど、今ようやくその言葉が真実だって実感した。[linebreak]正直、どうしたらいいか分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:I'd always heard people say that girls use tears as a weapon, but only now did I realize that it was true. To be honest, I didn't know what to do.[%p]"

msgid "11800:ただ気ばかりが焦って、オロオロしてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:I just stood there, half-stammering.[%p]"

msgid "11900:[name]拓巳[line]「い……」[%p]"
msgstr "11900:[name]拓巳[line]I...[%p]"

msgid "12000:一緒に行ってあげるよ、と言おうとしたけどできなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:I tried to say I'd go with her, but I couldn't.[%p]"

msgid "12100:もしもそう言った後で“本気にすんなよバーカ。キモい”とか言われたらどうしよう？[%p]"
msgstr "12100:What if I said yes, and then the next thing she said was, “Don't take me seriously, idiot. You're creepy.”[%p]"

msgid "12200:そんな被害妄想にとらわれて、声が出なくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:I was so scared of the idea that I was struck silent.[%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]優愛[line]「無理してくれなくていいです。わたしのワガママに、西條くんを付き合わせるのはよくないですし……ぐすっ」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]優愛[line]Y-You don't have to. It's not right to drag you along with me... sob.[%p]"

msgid "12400:なんだかさっきより瞳が潤んでるぞ……。[linebreak]今にも雫が目尻からこぼれ落ちそうだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:Her eyes were even wetter now. It felt like tears could start pouring from her eyes any second.[%p]"

msgid "12500:[name]拓巳[line]「い、行く……よ……」[%p]"
msgstr "12500:[name]拓巳[line]I-I'll go.[%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]優愛[line]「え？」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]優愛[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "12800:[name]優愛[line]「行って、もらえるんですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "12800:[name]優愛[line]You'll go?[%p]"

msgid "12900:仕方なくうなずく。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:I nodded, helplessly.[%p]"

msgid "13000:こうするしか、優愛を泣きやませる方法を思いつかなかった。[linebreak]まんまと罠にはめられた気がするけど……。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:It was the only way I could think of to get her to stop crying. The whole thing felt like a setup, but...[%p]"

msgid "13100:優愛はホッとしたように息をつくと、眼鏡を外して涙を拭った。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:She let out a sigh of relief and then took off her glasses to wipe away her tears.[%p]"

msgid "13200:[name]優愛[line]「断られて当然だと思ってたのに……。西條くん、ありがとうございます」[%p]"
msgstr "13200:[name]優愛[line]I was sure you were going to say no... Thank you, Nishijo![%p]"

msgid "13300:お礼を言ってきた……。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:She said thanks...[%p]"

msgid "13400:なんとか本格的に泣かせるまでには至らなかったみたいだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:I'd managed to keep her from crying, at least.[%p]"

msgid "13500:助かったのはこっちだよ……。[linebreak]はあ、なんでこんなに追い詰められてるんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:I got lucky, I guess. Whew... Why did this have to be so stressful?[%p]"

msgid "13600:くそぅ、三次元女め……油断大敵だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:You couldn't let your guard down around 3D girls for a minute, damn it.[%p]"

msgid "13700:[name]優愛[line]「行くとしたら、いつがいいでしょう？」[%p]"
msgstr "13700:[name]優愛[line]If we're going to go, when would be a good time?[%p]"

msgid "13800:しかも、さっきまでの悲しそうな表情がどこへやら。[linebreak]すっかり嬉しそうな顔になってるし。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:What happened to that sad expression of hers? Now she looked really happy.[%p]"

msgid "13900:やっぱり、嘘泣きだったんじゃないかな……。[linebreak]もしそうなら、女優なみの演技力だぞ。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:Maybe she was making it up the whole time. If so, she had a future as an actress.[%p]"

msgid "14000:[name]優愛[line]「星来ちゃんの新しいフィギュアは、もうすぐ発売なんですよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "14000:[name]優愛[line]Seira's new figure is coming out soon, right?[%p]"

msgid "14100:[name]拓巳[line]「う、うん。きっとすぐに完売しちゃう……だろうね」[%p]"
msgstr "14100:[name]拓巳[line]Y-Yeah. It'll probably sell out really fast.[%p]"

msgid "14200:[name]優愛[line]「だったら、早めに行った方がよさそうですね……」[%p]"
msgstr "14200:[name]優愛[line]Then we should go soon.[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]優愛[line]「明日とか……？」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]優愛[line]Tomorrow, maybe?[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "14500:確か今週の僕のスケジュールだと、明日は学校に行く日だ。今週はよりによって３回行かなくちゃいけないんだ。その分、来週は２回なんだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:According to my schedule, tomorrow was a school day. This week, I had to go three times. Of course, that meant next week, I only went twice.[%p]"

msgid "14600:明日はますます憂鬱な日になりそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:Tomorrow was going to be an even worse day than I thought.[%p]"

msgid "14700:でもすっかり行く気になってる優愛に“やっぱり行かない”なんて言ったらまた泣かれるかも……。[linebreak]うう、翻弄されてる……。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:But Yua looked really excited, and if I told her I changed my mind now, she might cry again. Ugh... she had me in her clutches.[%p]"

msgid "14800:[name]拓巳[line]「わ、分かったよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "14800:[name]拓巳[line]F-Fine.[%p]"

msgid "14900:渋々、了解した。[linebreak]優愛は嬉しそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:I reluctantly agreed. Yua looked happy.[%p]"

msgid "15000:そんな顔をしたって騙されないんだからな。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:But she couldn't fool me, okay?[%p]"

msgid "15100:[name]優愛[line]「西條くんは何組？\u3000明日、放課後に迎えに行きますよ」[%p]"
msgstr "15100:[name]優愛[line]What class are you in? I'll go there after school ends.[%p]"

msgid "15200:[name]拓巳[line]「……Ｂ組」[%p]"
msgstr "15200:[name]拓巳[line]Class B.[%p]"

msgid "15300:[name]優愛[line]「２年Ｂ組ですね。じゃあ、授業が終わったら待っててください」[%p]"
msgstr "15300:[name]優愛[line]2-B, right? Okay, I'll see you after class, then.[%p]"

msgid "15400:早く優愛に帰ってもらいたくて、僕はコクコクとうなずく。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:I nodded, hoping I could get her to leave.[%p]"

msgid "15500:女の子と、一緒に遊びに行く約束……。これって、夢とか妄想じゃないよなあ……？[%p]"
msgstr "15500:I was going somewhere with a girl... This wasn't a dream or a delusion, was it?[%p]"

msgid "15600:試しに頬をつねってみた。痛かった。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:I tried pinching myself. It hurt.[%p]"

msgid "15700:[name]優愛[line]「それじゃあ、長い間お邪魔しちゃって、すいませんでした。足、もし痛かったらお医者さんに行ってくださいね？」[%p]"
msgstr "15700:[name]優愛[line]All right. Sorry for staying so long. If your leg still hurts, go see a doctor, okay?[%p]"

msgid "15800:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、うん……」[%p]"
msgstr "15800:[name]拓巳[line]Oh, yeah...[%p]"

msgid "15900:僕はソファに座ったまま、優愛が出ていくのを見送る。[linebreak]優愛は部屋から出ていく直前、僕を振り返って小さく手を振った。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:I sat on the sofa and watched her go. Just before she left, she turned and waved at me.[%p]"

msgid "16000:[name]優愛[line]「西條くん、また明日」[%p]"
msgstr "16000:[name]優愛[line]See you tomorrow, Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "16100:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "16100:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "16200:[name]拓巳[line]「また明日、だってさ……」[%p]"
msgstr "16200:[name]拓巳[line]“See you tomorrow,” she said.[%p]"

msgid "16300:[name]拓巳[line]「しかも手を振ったりして……」[%p]"
msgstr "16300:[name]拓巳[line]And she even waved at me.[%p]"

msgid "16400:[name]拓巳[line]「…………ふひひ」[%p]"
msgstr "16400:[name]拓巳[line]... Fweheheh.[%p]"

msgid "16500:自然と頬が緩みそうになって、慌てて引き締めた。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:I felt a grin coming on, but forced myself to stop.[%p]"

msgid "16600:[name]拓巳[line]「あの女、絶対僕に惚れてる。間違いないね。ふひひ」[%p]"
msgstr "16600:[name]拓巳[line]She's in love with me. I'm sure of it. Fweheheh![%p]"

msgid "16700:[name]拓巳[line]「ま、付き合うか付き合わないかは僕に選択肢があるわけだし？\u3000あの女を情け容赦なく振ってやるさ」[%p]"
msgstr "16700:[name]拓巳[line]Well, it's up to me whether I actually date her or not, right? I'll just dump her. Brutally and without mercy.[%p]"

msgid "16800:[name]拓巳[line]「“お前は僕の女にふさわしくない。星来よりいい女になって出直してこい。まあ一生無理だけどな。なにしろ星来は永遠の１７歳だからな”みたいな。ふひひひひひひひ」[%p]"
msgstr "16800:[name]拓巳[line]“You're not worthy of being my girlfriend. Come back when you're a better girl than Seira. I bet that's impossible, though. Seira's going to be 17 years old forever, after all!” Something like that. Fweheheheheheh![%p]"

msgid "16900:星来たんよりいい女なんているもんか。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:No girl could be better than Seira-tan.[%p]"

msgid "17000:フィギュアを手に取って、頬ずりしてあげた。[linebreak]星来たんは嬉しそうだった。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:I picked up the figure and rubbed it against my cheeks. Seira-tan looked happy.[%p]"

